  <brief_title>Maintenance Treatment With Capecitabine Versus Observation in Breast Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Open-label, Randomized Phase III Trial, to Evaluate Efficacy of Maintenance Treatment With Capecitabine (X) Following Standard Adjuvant Chemotherapy, in Operable Breast Cancer Patients With Negative Hormone Receptor, Negative HER2 Tumours</official_title>
